description: This file is the entry point for a React application. It imports React and ReactDOM libraries, along with CSS styles and the main App component. It initializes the React root and renders the App component within StrictMode into the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering, targeting the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React components into the created root.
